* The TRAPEZIUS MUSCLE is triangular in shape, with the
base towards the spine, but the two muscles taken together
have the form of a trapezoid figure. The muscle has an
Origin extensive aponeurotic origin from the spines of the dorsal
otic. vertebræ and their supraspinous ligament, from the spinous
