On its anterior aspect, the abdomen Appearis for the most part convex, especially in fat bodies, whilst on the
on the sides, between the ribs and pelvis, the surface is some- the abwhat depressed. Along the middle line is a slight groove,
corresponding to the linea alba, which presents about its
