ARTICULATION OF THE ANKLE -. -Like the knee, the ankle
is a ginglymoid or hinge joint. In this instance the upper
surface of the astragalus is received into an arch formed by
the lower ends of the tibia and fibula, and the four ligaments
LIGAMENTS OF THE ANKLE- JOINT. 695
belonging to this kind of articulation connect together the
bones.
